  "anvaya": "దేవీ ఆపతత్ తత్ శూలం దృష్ట్వా శూలం అముఞ్చత। తేన తత్ శూలం శతధా నీతం, సః మహాసురః చ శతధా నీతః।",
  "tatparyam": {
    "english": "Seeing the spear coming toward her, the Goddess released her own spear. By it, that spear was shattered into a hundred pieces, and so was the great demon.",
